dden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pta1665702586322.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pta1665702586322.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pta1665702586322.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pta1665702586322\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Is External\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pta1665702586322__section_w2902ab1b5b1_w2903ab1b5_w2904ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"pta1665702586322__table_d11489e1_d11490e1_d11491e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pta1665702586322__table_d11489e1_d11490e1_d11491e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"pta1665702586322__table_d11489e1_d11490e1_d11491e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pta1665702586322__table_d11489e1_d11490e1_d11491e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pta1665702586322__table_d11489e1_d11490e1_d11491e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The data of the Component Field can be stored in a database, or it can be exchanged with other components via entity or occurrence parameters.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pta1665702586322__table_d11489e1_d11490e1_d11491e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">F</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"pta1665702586322__table_d11489e1_d11490e1_d11491e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The Component Field cannot be externalized.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pta1665702586322__section_c5v_yxq_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1136125e121\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pta1665702586322__p_d99203e1_d99204e1_d99205e1\">In most cases, the value of <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Is\n               External</span> is determined by the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Database Behavior</span>\n            property of its parent entity. By default, if an entity's <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Database\n               Behavior</span> property is <code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code>, each of its fields has its\n               <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Is External</span> property set to <code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code>, and vice\n            versa.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pta1665702586322__p_d99206e1_d99207e1_d99208e1\">However, if you are defining a component that needs to\n            exchange information by means of entity or occurrence parameters, the fields to be\n            included in the data exchange must have <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Is External</span> set to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">T</code>, even if the parent entity is not a database entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pta1665702586322__p_d99209e1_d99210e1_d99211e1\">Use Static or Control fields for buttons and fields\n            containing static data, such as images or labels. In these fields, the field values are\n            retained when the parent component entity is saved, or cleared, or when occurrences are\n            added or deleted.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pta1665702586322__p_d99212e1_d99213e1_d99214e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">B</code> Field contents are not stored in the database and are not repeated in\n            entity occurrences.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pta1665702586322__p_d99215e1_d99216e1_d99217e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">X</code> Field contents are not stored in the database, and are not repeated\n            in entity occurrences.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pta1665702586322__p_d99218e1_d99219e1_d99220e1\">In Form components, the normal Uniface checks are not\n            performed for Control fields.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pta1665702586322__p_d99221e1_d99222e1_d99223e1\">The behavior of Static and Control fields is the same\n            in all components except Forms. In Form components, the normal Uniface checks are not\n            performed for Control fields. For example, by defining the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Quit</span>\n            button as a Control field, you can leave a component even when some of the fields\n            contain incorrect data.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pta1665702586322__section_qwg_3ks_qwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1136125e183\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pta1665702586322__ul_aph_jks_qwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pta1665702586322__li_d39908e1_d39909e1_d39910e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lym1665702585074.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lym1665702585074.html\" title=\"A Field is a Development Object that represents a unit of data in an Entity. This could represent a column in a DBMS table or data that is not stored in the database, such as a derived field or a user interface control. Its associated properties define the way it is stored, its GUI representation, and default behavior.\">Field</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipj1665702760143.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>entity</a><p>Uniface data type for transferring occurrences of entities between components.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ndc1665702760212.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>occurrence</a><p>Uniface data type containing a single occurrence of an entity. For use in parameters.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615279\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3615279\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Is External Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Is External Determines whether the Field's data can be externalized outside the component, either by storing it in a database or passing it in an entity or occurrence parameter. Value Description T The data of the Component Field can be stored in a database, or it can be exchanged with other components via entity or occurrence parameters. F The Component Field cannot be externalized. Description In most cases, the value of Is External is determined by the Database Behavior property of its parent entity. By default, if an entity's Database Behavior property is T , each of its fields has its Is External property set to T , and vice versa. However, if you are defining a component that needs to exchange information by means of entity or occurrence parameters, the fields to be included in the data exchange must have Is External set to T , even if the parent entity is not a database entity. Use Static or Control fields for buttons and fields containing static data, such as images or labels. In these fields, the field values are retained when the parent component entity is saved, or cleared, or when occurrences are added or deleted. B Field contents are not stored in the database and are not repeated in entity occurrences. X Field contents are not stored in the database, and are not repeated in entity occurrences. In Form components, the normal Uniface checks are not performed for Control fields. The behavior of Static and Control fields is the same in all components except Forms. In Form components, the normal Uniface checks are not performed for Control fields. For example, by defining the Quit button as a Control field, you can leave a component even when some of the fields contain incorrect data. Applies To Field Related Links entity Uniface data type for transferring occurrences of entities between components. occurrence Uniface data type containing a single occurrence of an entity. For use in parameters. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}